The perfect way to start your day off on the right foot, this Tropical Mango Smoothie is filled with fresh flavours guaranteed to make you feel like you’re relaxing on the beach with a chilled Pina Colada. It is also a good source of vitamins C and A, fibre and proteins The best part about it is that it’s kid-friendly and totally easy to make. *The recipe makes one smoothie. Tropical mango pineapple smoothie. Photo credit: Joyful Healthy Eats Be sure to take a picture if you make this recipe and tag #GuardianLifeNg when you share. We would love to see what you make.